1
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:19,394
Careful, Thor.
You're looking a bit unsteady.

2
00:00:19,436 --> 00:00:20,312
Right.

3
00:00:20,354 --> 00:00:21,563
Ah. Good form,

4
00:00:21,605 --> 00:00:23,815
but I think you could stand
to push yourself further.

5
00:00:23,857 --> 00:00:25,108
Yes sir.

6
00:00:27,611 --> 00:00:28,612
[MERLIN gasps]

7
00:00:28,654 --> 00:00:30,113
[MERLIN]
That's too much power, Lyn!

8
00:00:30,155 --> 00:00:31,156
[LYN]
Huh?

9
00:00:31,198 --> 00:00:32,241
[MERLIN]
You'll lose control!

10
00:00:32,282 --> 00:00:34,493
[LYN]
Oh. I guess I'd better stop.

11
00:00:34,535 --> 00:00:35,702
[MARIA, MERLIN, YURI sigh]

12
00:00:35,744 --> 00:00:36,620
[YURI]
Be careful!

13
00:00:36,662 --> 00:00:39,122
At this rate, you'll mess up
all of our hair again!

14
00:00:43,710 --> 00:00:45,754
[SHIN] Thanks to the
two of them helping out,

15
00:00:45,796 --> 00:00:47,881
this camp is already
turning out a lot better

16
00:00:47,923 --> 00:00:49,758
than I'd expected.

17
00:00:53,887 --> 00:00:56,515
They're firing freely.
No chants required.

18
00:00:56,557 --> 00:00:59,685
They'll put the Court Magic
Division right out of business.

19
00:00:59,726 --> 00:01:00,936
[SHIN]
They're strong,

20
00:01:00,978 --> 00:01:03,814
but they'll still have a rough
time against demonoids.

21
00:01:03,855 --> 00:01:05,774
Yes. I think you're right.

22
00:01:05,816 --> 00:01:10,237
My. This is horrible.
The whole world is in danger.

23
00:01:10,279 --> 00:01:13,490
[SHIN] Demons run rampant over
what was once the Empire.

24
00:01:13,532 --> 00:01:16,577
If we hope to stand up against
their overwhelming power,

25
00:01:16,618 --> 00:01:19,621
then everyone at this
camp needs to get much stronger.

26
00:01:19,663 --> 00:01:23,000
And yes, that's
including myself.

27
00:01:23,041 --> 00:01:24,751
[ALL]
Huh?

28
00:01:24,793 --> 00:01:25,794
[SHIN]
Huh?

29
00:02:58,762 --> 00:03:00,681
[SHIN grumbles]

30
00:03:00,722 --> 00:03:02,057
[MARIA]
Keep your guards up, everyone!

31
00:03:02,099 --> 00:03:05,018
Make some magic barriers and
give 'em everything you've got!

32
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:07,062
[SHIN] Aw, I don't think
it'll hit you guys.

33
00:03:07,104 --> 00:03:08,897
[ALICE]
You don't think?!

34
00:03:08,939 --> 00:03:09,940
[SHIN gasps]

35
00:03:11,149 --> 00:03:13,610
She's right. Better safe
than slaughtered.

36
00:03:13,652 --> 00:03:14,903
We all know what Shin can do.

37
00:03:14,945 --> 00:03:17,614
C'mon, I told you,
it'll be fine.

38
00:03:18,657 --> 00:03:21,118
[SHIN] I just wanna
test out this idea.

39
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:25,372
Hydrogen, oxygen, and
something more volatile.

40
00:03:27,708 --> 00:03:29,042
[GROUP gasps]

41
00:03:30,085 --> 00:03:32,421
That looks super cool,
but what does it do?

42
00:03:32,462 --> 00:03:33,839
[SHIN]
It's not done.

43
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,882
This is the part
that really counts.

44
00:03:35,924 --> 00:03:37,968
Hope I don't screw it up.

45
00:03:39,886 --> 00:03:42,347
Kay! Let's brace for impact!

46
00:03:42,389 --> 00:03:43,223
[SHIN]
Up to now,

47
00:03:43,265 --> 00:03:46,017
the blast would spread out
as it got further away.

48
00:03:46,059 --> 00:03:48,353
I need to set up a
single outlet point.

49
00:03:48,395 --> 00:03:51,231
Contain it as it builds
for as long as I can...

50
00:03:51,273 --> 00:03:53,984
...and then release it!

51
00:03:54,025 --> 00:03:55,360
[ALL gasp]

52
00:03:59,448 --> 00:04:00,866
[GROUP]
Uh...?

53
00:04:00,907 --> 00:04:03,160
Almost forgot what
a monster he is.

54
00:04:03,201 --> 00:04:05,245
I think that's my
strongest spell yet!

55
00:04:05,287 --> 00:04:06,246
[MELIDA]
Idiot!

56
00:04:06,288 --> 00:04:08,790
Why would you possibly
need that much force?!

57
00:04:08,832 --> 00:04:11,668
[ALICE] Heh. Am I having
a weird dream right now?

58
00:04:11,710 --> 00:04:12,794
[LYN]
This is real.

59
00:04:12,836 --> 00:04:15,797
Yeah. I didn't realize the
spell would be that strong.

60
00:04:15,839 --> 00:04:17,758
‐‐[MELIDA hisses]
‐‐Ah! I'm sorry!

61
00:04:17,799 --> 00:04:20,177
It's strange.
Strong as that blast was,

62
00:04:20,218 --> 00:04:22,804
I would've expected us
to feel more on our end.

63
00:04:22,846 --> 00:04:24,097
Right. I don't think he

64
00:04:24,139 --> 00:04:26,850
used much more firepower,
he just condensed it.

65
00:04:26,892 --> 00:04:28,643
That seems accurate to me.

66
00:04:28,685 --> 00:04:31,313
I've come a long way,
but up against that spell?

67
00:04:31,354 --> 00:04:32,606
I would get destroyed.

68
00:04:32,647 --> 00:04:35,108
True, but I'd never risk
letting that spell hit you.

69
00:04:35,150 --> 00:04:36,401
Well then what was
all that about

70
00:04:36,443 --> 00:04:38,320
"I don't think it'll
hit you guys"?

71
00:04:38,361 --> 00:04:39,988
Sounds pretty risky to me!

72
00:04:40,030 --> 00:04:41,406
[MELIDA]
That'll be all for today.

73
00:04:41,448 --> 00:04:43,575
Let's head back
to the manor now.

74
00:04:43,617 --> 00:04:44,951
[GROUP]
Yes, ma'am.

75
00:04:45,952 --> 00:04:47,454
[AUGUST]
I hate to trouble you, Shin,

76
00:04:47,496 --> 00:04:49,873
but could you make me
a Gate to the castle?

77
00:04:49,915 --> 00:04:50,999
How come?

78
00:04:51,041 --> 00:04:53,877
I tried to track the demon
situation from camp,

79
00:04:53,919 --> 00:04:54,753
but it's tough.

80
00:04:54,795 --> 00:04:56,379
I need to talk to my father.

81
00:04:56,421 --> 00:04:58,507
[SHIN]
Okay. I'll come with.

82
00:05:01,551 --> 00:05:03,678
[MALE GUARD A]
Your Highness! You're here!

83
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,639
What's wrong?
Has anything happened?

84
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:08,058
[ELISABET] I don't know, August.
Why don't you tell me?

85
00:05:08,099 --> 00:05:09,351
Huh?

86
00:05:11,561 --> 00:05:12,604
[ELISABET grunts]

87
00:05:12,646 --> 00:05:14,397
Oh, Ellie!

88
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,315
Who?

89
00:05:15,357 --> 00:05:18,026
Oh, um... She's my fiancée.

90
00:05:18,068 --> 00:05:20,403
[SHIN]
Hm? Huh? Eh? Ahh?!

91
00:05:20,445 --> 00:05:22,113
Your fiancée?!

92
00:05:22,155 --> 00:05:25,075
Are you seriously engaged?
I didn't know that.

93
00:05:25,116 --> 00:05:27,410
Of course you didn't.
I never told you.

94
00:05:27,452 --> 00:05:29,496
[ELISABET] Well, if you won't
introduce your friend,

95
00:05:29,538 --> 00:05:31,706
I guess I'll take charge.

96
00:05:32,916 --> 00:05:33,917
[SHIN, AUGUST grunt]

97
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:35,544
[ELISABET]
You must be Shin.

98
00:05:35,585 --> 00:05:38,547
I hoped I might get to meet
our Kingdom's new hero.

99
00:05:38,588 --> 00:05:41,258
I'm the second eldest
daughter of Duke Koralle,

100
00:05:41,299 --> 00:05:43,552
and I'm Prince August's fiancée.

101
00:05:43,593 --> 00:05:46,513
I am known in court
as Elisabet von Koralle.

102
00:05:46,555 --> 00:05:48,765
It's a pleasure to make
your acquaintance.

103
00:05:48,807 --> 00:05:50,809
[SHIN]
It's nice to meet you, too.

104
00:05:50,851 --> 00:05:53,019
You care to tell me what
you're doing here, Ellie?

105
00:05:53,061 --> 00:05:55,188
[ELISABET]
Spending time with my betrothed!

106
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:57,858
Or so I thought, except
you left me and May behind

107
00:05:57,899 --> 00:05:59,943
while you trounced
off to summer camp.

108
00:05:59,985 --> 00:06:01,069
Wait, who's May?

109
00:06:01,111 --> 00:06:02,696
[AUGUST]
My younger sister.

110
00:06:02,737 --> 00:06:04,447
[MAY]
That's right!

111
00:06:04,489 --> 00:06:06,074
[AUGUST]
Do you plan to shame me too?

112
00:06:06,116 --> 00:06:08,535
Uh! You're not turning
the tables this time!

113
00:06:08,577 --> 00:06:10,829
How could you up
and leave me here?

114
00:06:10,871 --> 00:06:12,330
I heard that Melida the Guru

115
00:06:12,372 --> 00:06:14,040
is one of the teachers
at that camp!

116
00:06:14,082 --> 00:06:16,835
You know how much I like her,
but you left me behind anyway!

117
00:06:16,877 --> 00:06:19,504
You didn't even talk to me
about it, how could you?!

118
00:06:19,546 --> 00:06:20,505
Can't help it.

119
00:06:20,547 --> 00:06:23,341
You're much too fun to watch
when you get wound up like this.

120
00:06:23,383 --> 00:06:24,384
[MAY]
You're so mean!

121
00:06:24,426 --> 00:06:25,218
This isn't fair!

122
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:28,179
I want to see Lady Melida
way more than you do!

123
00:06:28,221 --> 00:06:29,472
You mean Granny?

124
00:06:29,514 --> 00:06:33,894
Oh, right! Um. Forgive my
rudeness, Master Shin!

125
00:06:33,935 --> 00:06:36,271
I'm big brother August's
younger sister.

126
00:06:36,313 --> 00:06:40,775
My name is May von Earlsheid.
Um, you see, I‐I'm...

127
00:06:40,817 --> 00:06:42,569
I'm a huge Lady Melida fan!

128
00:06:42,611 --> 00:06:43,653
Oh. Cool.

129
00:06:43,695 --> 00:06:46,156
Hi May, it's nice to meet you.

130
00:06:46,197 --> 00:06:48,909
Aug and I pretty much act
as though we're family,

131
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:51,411
so feel free to think of me
in the same way.

132
00:06:51,453 --> 00:06:54,831
[MAY] Uh? Then, can I
call you big brother?

133
00:06:54,873 --> 00:06:57,500
Hm. Well it's better
than "Master Shin."

134
00:06:57,542 --> 00:06:59,628
So, it's okay then?

135
00:06:59,669 --> 00:07:00,837
[SHIN]
Mm‐hm.

136
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:02,213
[gasps]

137
00:07:02,255 --> 00:07:03,298
[giggles]

138
00:07:03,340 --> 00:07:06,009
I'll finally have a big brother
who isn't mean to me!

139
00:07:06,051 --> 00:07:07,469
[SHIN laughs]

140
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:09,554
So, what can I do for you?

141
00:07:09,596 --> 00:07:11,056
[MAY, ELISABET]
Hmm.

142
00:07:11,097 --> 00:07:12,265
We've made a decision.

143
00:07:12,307 --> 00:07:15,018
The two of us are going to join
you at this summer camp.

144
00:07:15,060 --> 00:07:15,852
Right.

145
00:07:15,894 --> 00:07:17,270
Don't be foolish!

146
00:07:17,312 --> 00:07:20,023
It may be a camp,
but it's not for fun!

147
00:07:20,065 --> 00:07:23,234
There's no way you'll get
permission to come with me!

148
00:07:23,276 --> 00:07:26,363
I grant them my permission
to go with you.

149
00:07:26,404 --> 00:07:27,280
Are you joking?

150
00:07:27,322 --> 00:07:28,114
[ELISABET, MAY laugh]

151
00:07:28,156 --> 00:07:30,325
I knew you'd come through
for us, Daddy!

152
00:07:30,367 --> 00:07:32,035
The Klode Springs
are well‐protected,

153
00:07:32,077 --> 00:07:35,163
as long as Master Merlin
and Lady Melida stay there.

154
00:07:35,205 --> 00:07:36,998
These two should be fine.

155
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,209
Let the girls have some
fun at the Hot Springs.

156
00:07:39,250 --> 00:07:41,169
Take Shin's gate
there for safety.

157
00:07:41,211 --> 00:07:42,128
On a side note,

158
00:07:42,170 --> 00:07:44,506
I've already gotten
permission from my father.

159
00:07:44,547 --> 00:07:46,967
‐‐[AUGUST] Uhh...
‐‐[SHIN laughs]

160
00:07:48,426 --> 00:07:50,053
[SHIN]
Ellie? May?

161
00:07:50,095 --> 00:07:52,806
You can come across. It's safe.

162
00:07:52,847 --> 00:07:54,516
[BOTH gasp]

163
00:07:54,557 --> 00:07:56,685
[MAY] We were in the castle
just a moment ago!

164
00:07:56,726 --> 00:07:58,144
How'd we move so fast?

165
00:07:58,186 --> 00:07:59,396
[AUGUST]
I know you're excited

166
00:07:59,437 --> 00:08:01,147
but try not to stray
from the group.

167
00:08:01,189 --> 00:08:03,191
[MAY grumbles]

168
00:08:03,233 --> 00:08:05,026
[SHIN]
Take my hand. Kay, sis?

169
00:08:05,068 --> 00:08:07,529
Can't let ya get lost.
I'd be in big trouble.

170
00:08:07,570 --> 00:08:08,905
[gasps] Okay!

171
00:08:08,947 --> 00:08:13,576
May, do as Shin says.
Don't make any problems for him.

172
00:08:13,618 --> 00:08:15,036
‐‐Also...
‐‐[ELISABET] Hm?

173
00:08:15,078 --> 00:08:18,456
Like I told you, this camp
is for magic training.

174
00:08:18,498 --> 00:08:21,376
And training is what I plan
to focus on while I'm there.

175
00:08:21,418 --> 00:08:23,169
I don't intend to
get in the way.

176
00:08:23,211 --> 00:08:25,422
Though, I may have to
take some measures

177
00:08:25,463 --> 00:08:27,507
to ensure that you
stay free of pests.

178
00:08:27,549 --> 00:08:29,050
Oh. Yeah, I get it.

179
00:08:29,092 --> 00:08:31,720
You're talking about all our
female classmates, right?

180
00:08:31,761 --> 00:08:33,972
Are ya worried that one
of 'em might make a move?

181
00:08:34,014 --> 00:08:34,889
No.

182
00:08:34,931 --> 00:08:36,516
The girls aren't a threat to me.

183
00:08:36,558 --> 00:08:39,561
If you must know who it is that
I do not trust with my fiancé‐‐

184
00:08:39,602 --> 00:08:42,897
then check a mirror!
'Cause it's you!

185
00:08:42,939 --> 00:08:44,649
[SHIN yells]

186
00:08:44,691 --> 00:08:47,152
[ELISABET] You should hear
August at dinner. Really...

187
00:08:47,193 --> 00:08:49,738
Every time he opens his mouth,
it's "Shin invented this,"

188
00:08:49,779 --> 00:08:51,197
or "Shin saved the
kingdom from that."

189
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:52,824
You're all he talks about!

190
00:08:52,866 --> 00:08:54,868
Can you blame me
for being suspicious?

191
00:08:54,909 --> 00:08:56,286
[SHIN]
Wait, really?!

192
00:08:56,327 --> 00:08:57,746
It's not what you
seem to be thinking.

193
00:08:57,787 --> 00:08:59,581
That never even crossed
my mind 'til now,

194
00:08:59,622 --> 00:09:00,957
and we've been in
a bath together.

195
00:09:00,999 --> 00:09:03,960
[MAY] Oh! I'm thinking
about adult situations now!

196
00:09:04,002 --> 00:09:07,047
Well, I was quite glad
that we became friends.

197
00:09:07,088 --> 00:09:09,174
You're someone I can
be myself around.

198
00:09:09,215 --> 00:09:11,468
[ELISABET growls]
What's that mean?!

199
00:09:11,509 --> 00:09:13,553
Why don't you feel like you
can be yourself around me?!

200
00:09:13,595 --> 00:09:14,888
Is it because of my temper?!

201
00:09:14,929 --> 00:09:17,390
I'm myself with you, too.

202
00:09:17,432 --> 00:09:19,642
When I'm with you,
I feel at peace.

203
00:09:19,684 --> 00:09:20,852
[ELISABET gasps]

204
00:09:21,811 --> 00:09:22,979
[AUGUST] But I'm getting
to horse around

205
00:09:23,021 --> 00:09:24,355
with another guy for once.

206
00:09:24,397 --> 00:09:27,025
It's a new experience,
so I got carried away.

207
00:09:27,067 --> 00:09:29,944
But it doesn't replace
what we have.

208
00:09:29,986 --> 00:09:31,029
Please understand, Ellie.

209
00:09:31,071 --> 00:09:33,364
So, that's all that's going on?

210
00:09:33,406 --> 00:09:36,367
Besides, Shin's already
found himself a woman.

211
00:09:36,409 --> 00:09:37,869
You mean like a girlfriend?

212
00:09:37,911 --> 00:09:39,954
[SHIN] Uh?! What the
heck are you saying?

213
00:09:39,996 --> 00:09:41,623
I don't have a girlfriend yet.

214
00:09:41,664 --> 00:09:42,916
But you know who you want.

215
00:09:42,957 --> 00:09:44,417
[gasping]

216
00:09:44,459 --> 00:09:48,505
Look, now's the time.
You need to make things clear.

217
00:09:48,546 --> 00:09:50,256
What do I need to make clear?

218
00:09:50,298 --> 00:09:52,383
Where it is that you two stand.

219
00:09:52,425 --> 00:09:54,177
She's feeling
the same way you are.

220
00:09:54,219 --> 00:09:56,888
Everything'll work out.
Just talk to her.

221
00:09:56,930 --> 00:09:58,598
[SHIN]
She feels the same...?

222
00:09:58,640 --> 00:10:00,517
Sure, Sizilien's nice to me,

223
00:10:00,558 --> 00:10:03,645
but that's only because
Sizilien's a nice person.

224
00:10:03,686 --> 00:10:05,063
Wait, I don't see
how you could know

225
00:10:05,105 --> 00:10:07,023
that she has feeling for me too.

226
00:10:07,065 --> 00:10:08,441
I see it in her eyes.

227
00:10:08,483 --> 00:10:10,318
[SHIN] How can you say
that for sure though?

228
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:13,613
What if you're mistaken somehow?
That would be so awkward!

229
00:10:13,655 --> 00:10:15,782
[AUGUST] Are you fine with
things as they are then?

230
00:10:15,824 --> 00:10:18,660
It's called a confession
for a reason, it's risky.

231
00:10:18,701 --> 00:10:20,036
And it takes courage.

232
00:10:20,078 --> 00:10:22,622
Something I had thought
you had plenty of.

233
00:10:22,664 --> 00:10:25,291
You could wait though.
Force her to risk her dignity.

234
00:10:25,333 --> 00:10:27,335
I don't know, it's tough.

235
00:10:27,377 --> 00:10:29,462
I've been close to Ellie
since we were kids.

236
00:10:29,504 --> 00:10:31,631
Now we're set to be
husband and wife,

237
00:10:31,673 --> 00:10:33,341
but even we have
misunderstandings

238
00:10:33,383 --> 00:10:34,926
of this nature sometimes.

239
00:10:34,968 --> 00:10:36,094
I would appreciate it

240
00:10:36,136 --> 00:10:39,013
if you avoided using me
as an example for this.

241
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:46,187
[SIZILIEN]
You two are joining our camp?

242
00:10:46,229 --> 00:10:47,605
Yes, as fate would have it.

243
00:10:47,647 --> 00:10:51,025
Sorry, but uh, would you mind
putting them up here, Klode?

244
00:10:51,067 --> 00:10:53,194
[SIZILIEN]
Not at all. It's no problem.

245
00:10:53,236 --> 00:10:55,238
We shan't get in the
way of your training.

246
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,573
‐‐[MAY giggles]
‐‐[SHIN] Uh?

247
00:10:56,614 --> 00:10:58,158
Is everything okay, Shin?

248
00:10:58,199 --> 00:10:59,242
Uh. Yeah, I'm fine.

249
00:10:59,284 --> 00:11:00,952
Just havin' an
average, normal day.

250
00:11:00,994 --> 00:11:02,704
[SIZILIEN]
I'm glad to hear it.

251
00:11:02,745 --> 00:11:05,915
Ah. So all of that talk
before was about Sizilien.

252
00:11:05,957 --> 00:11:07,792
You mean the two of
them are together?

253
00:11:07,834 --> 00:11:08,626
What a cute couple!

254
00:11:08,668 --> 00:11:10,962
‐‐[SHIN sputters]
‐‐Wait?! What?

255
00:11:11,004 --> 00:11:13,339
Ahh! Don't listen to them!

256
00:11:21,973 --> 00:11:24,517
My name is Elisabet
von Koralle, ma'am.

257
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:27,687
I'm big brother August's
little sister May von Earlsheid.

258
00:11:27,729 --> 00:11:29,647
And... I...

259
00:11:29,689 --> 00:11:32,066
Yeah, so...
May's a big fan of yours.

260
00:11:32,108 --> 00:11:32,901
[MAY gasping]

261
00:11:32,942 --> 00:11:35,069
Isn't that sweet?

262
00:11:35,111 --> 00:11:37,864
Sorry to disappoint,
but I'm just an old lady now.

263
00:11:37,906 --> 00:11:39,574
No, I'm not disappointed at all!

264
00:11:39,616 --> 00:11:41,951
Um. Not to be a bother, but...

265
00:11:41,993 --> 00:11:45,330
I wonder if... you would
let me... take your hand?

266
00:11:45,371 --> 00:11:47,040
[MELIDA chuckles]
Of course, dear.

267
00:11:47,081 --> 00:11:48,041
[gasps]

268
00:11:48,082 --> 00:11:51,127
Young ladies like you
are so incredibly adorable.

269
00:11:51,169 --> 00:11:53,254
Boys like Shin just
aren't that cute.

270
00:11:53,296 --> 00:11:54,339
[MERLIN laughs]

271
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:57,217
You used to think I was cute.
You even held my hand.

272
00:11:57,258 --> 00:11:59,010
Did it all the time
when I was little.

273
00:11:59,052 --> 00:12:00,595
[MELIDA]
That was for safety.

274
00:12:00,637 --> 00:12:02,597
I never knew what
you'd get into.

275
00:12:02,639 --> 00:12:04,849
So, I had to keep you
nice and close.

276
00:12:04,891 --> 00:12:05,683
[SHIN grumbles]

277
00:12:05,725 --> 00:12:07,685
I can only imagine what
that must've been like.

278
00:12:07,727 --> 00:12:08,603
[SHIN]
Huh?

279
00:12:08,645 --> 00:12:11,439
I bet little Shin must've given
her a whole lot of headaches.

280
00:12:11,481 --> 00:12:13,107
She did what she could.

281
00:12:13,149 --> 00:12:15,568
There's no harder job
than raising a child.

282
00:12:15,610 --> 00:12:19,364
Honestly, I just pray that when
I have children they're normal.

283
00:12:19,405 --> 00:12:21,241
Hey, Shin, they don't mean‐‐

284
00:12:21,282 --> 00:12:23,076
[SHIN]
Yeah, they do, but it's fine.

285
00:12:23,117 --> 00:12:25,203
I'm sure you're
thinking the same.

286
00:12:25,245 --> 00:12:26,621
N‐No!

287
00:12:26,663 --> 00:12:28,957
That's not how I think
of you at all, Shin!

288
00:12:28,998 --> 00:12:31,793
I think that all our children
will be adorable!

289
00:12:31,834 --> 00:12:32,627
I know it!

290
00:12:32,669 --> 00:12:34,629
And I would be glad
to hold their hands!

291
00:12:34,671 --> 00:12:36,965
[GROUP gasps]

292
00:12:37,006 --> 00:12:38,633
[stammers]

293
00:12:38,675 --> 00:12:40,176
Did I really say that?

294
00:12:40,218 --> 00:12:41,386
Oh, no.

295
00:12:41,427 --> 00:12:43,096
Nice power play, Sizilien.

296
00:12:43,137 --> 00:12:44,931
[ALICE]
Kissy, kissy!

297
00:12:44,973 --> 00:12:47,183
Wow! You're so bold!

298
00:12:47,225 --> 00:12:48,768
Talk about a huge implosion.

299
00:12:48,810 --> 00:12:52,188
[whimpering]

300
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:53,773
[screams]

301
00:12:53,815 --> 00:12:55,733
[door clicks, slams]

302
00:12:55,775 --> 00:12:57,819
Well? Do you get it now?

303
00:12:57,860 --> 00:12:58,861
Yeah.

304
00:12:58,903 --> 00:13:01,864
I'm not so dense that I don't
get it when she says that.

305
00:13:01,906 --> 00:13:03,700
But note that you
are dense enough

306
00:13:03,741 --> 00:13:05,326
that she had to say all that.

307
00:13:05,368 --> 00:13:06,869
[SHIN]
Uh.

308
00:13:06,911 --> 00:13:08,746
[AUGUST]
Well, good luck.

309
00:13:08,788 --> 00:13:10,123
[SHIN]
Thanks.

310
00:13:23,845 --> 00:13:25,013
Uh?

311
00:13:27,932 --> 00:13:29,392
[SHIN sighs]

312
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:34,647
Oh. Hi, Shin.

313
00:13:34,689 --> 00:13:36,482
Um. What's going on?

314
00:13:36,524 --> 00:13:38,109
[SHIN]
Nothing too interesting.

315
00:13:38,151 --> 00:13:40,903
Just got out of the hot spring
and thought I'd cool off.

316
00:13:40,945 --> 00:13:44,073
Same here.
That water really is warm.

317
00:13:44,115 --> 00:13:45,408
I'll say.

318
00:13:45,450 --> 00:13:46,826
[wind blows]

319
00:13:51,289 --> 00:13:53,041
[SHIN, SIZILIEN laugh]

320
00:13:55,335 --> 00:13:57,295
‐‐[SIZILIEN] Listen.
‐‐[SHIN] Huh?

321
00:13:57,337 --> 00:13:59,589
I'd like to apologize
for earlier.

322
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,923
What?

323
00:14:00,965 --> 00:14:04,761
Oh. Thanks, but you have
nothing to be sorry for.

324
00:14:04,802 --> 00:14:05,928
I was really flattered.

325
00:14:05,970 --> 00:14:08,389
[gasps]

326
00:14:08,431 --> 00:14:10,308
Can I ask you something?

327
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:13,478
Do you remember
the day that we met?

328
00:14:13,519 --> 00:14:15,480
Yeah. Of course I do.

329
00:14:15,521 --> 00:14:16,731
I was with Maria.

330
00:14:16,773 --> 00:14:19,400
We got held up by
some demon hunters.

331
00:14:19,442 --> 00:14:22,111
And when I asked if they
were bothering you.

332
00:14:22,153 --> 00:14:24,947
She said, "We're extremely
frickin' bothered!"

333
00:14:24,989 --> 00:14:27,325
[BOTH laugh]

334
00:14:27,367 --> 00:14:28,618
[SIZILIEN]
And ever since,

335
00:14:28,659 --> 00:14:31,746
you've done nothing but help me
in every way you could.

336
00:14:31,788 --> 00:14:33,247
[SHIN]
The thing is,

337
00:14:33,289 --> 00:14:34,415
when I first saw you,

338
00:14:34,457 --> 00:14:37,043
it was like‐‐like I'd been
struck by lightning.

339
00:14:37,085 --> 00:14:38,002
Huh?

340
00:14:38,044 --> 00:14:41,297
Because you were
just that cute.

341
00:14:43,633 --> 00:14:45,551
You know, I had
a similar moment.

342
00:14:45,593 --> 00:14:47,637
When I first saw you, I, uh...

343
00:14:47,678 --> 00:14:49,764
I thought that you
were very handsome.

344
00:14:49,806 --> 00:14:51,891
[SHIN]
Wait. You mean it?!

345
00:14:51,933 --> 00:14:53,351
[SIZILIEN]
Yes.

346
00:14:54,519 --> 00:14:55,561
Sizilien.

347
00:14:55,603 --> 00:14:57,605
Oh, uh, yeah?

348
00:15:00,024 --> 00:15:01,109
I love you.

349
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:02,485
[gasps]

350
00:15:06,447 --> 00:15:08,658
[SIZILIEN]
That makes me so happy.

351
00:15:08,699 --> 00:15:12,120
You're always so nice
to me, but I thought...

352
00:15:12,161 --> 00:15:16,207
...that you were just doing that
because you're a nice boy.

353
00:15:16,249 --> 00:15:19,210
Did the way I acted really
lead you to think that?

354
00:15:19,252 --> 00:15:22,547
Yeah, but now you're
saying that isn't true!

355
00:15:22,588 --> 00:15:24,966
I was special to you.

356
00:15:25,007 --> 00:15:27,051
I feel the way you do.

357
00:15:27,093 --> 00:15:29,387
I love you too. 'Kay, Shin?

358
00:15:29,429 --> 00:15:30,847
Sizilien.

359
00:15:30,888 --> 00:15:31,764
[SIZILIEN]
Yes?

360
00:15:31,806 --> 00:15:35,393
Would you...
wanna be my girlfriend?

361
00:15:35,435 --> 00:15:37,103
Yeah.

362
00:15:42,316 --> 00:15:43,443
‐‐[MARIA] Whoa!
‐‐[SHIN, SIZILIEN gasp]

363
00:15:43,484 --> 00:15:45,027
[GIRLS groan]

364
00:15:45,069 --> 00:15:46,320
[BOYS gasp]

365
00:15:46,362 --> 00:15:48,948
[GROUP laughs]

366
00:15:48,990 --> 00:15:50,700
‐‐[ALICE] Well that was fun.
‐‐[LYN] Did they see us?

367
00:15:50,741 --> 00:15:52,118
‐‐[JULIUS] I can explain?
‐‐[THOR] Congratulations?

368
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:54,162
Wait... What in
the world's going on?

369
00:15:54,203 --> 00:15:56,456
Did every single one of
you come to spy on us?

370
00:15:56,497 --> 00:15:58,166
[ALICE, MARIA] There was
no way we were about to

371
00:15:58,207 --> 00:15:59,542
miss a massive event like this!

372
00:15:59,584 --> 00:16:01,836
Why the heck're you
yelling at me?!

373
00:16:01,878 --> 00:16:04,630
