a celebration tomorrow!

385
00:16:27,778 --> 00:16:30,072
[SHIN]
Even he was watching?

386
00:16:30,114 --> 00:16:31,115
[sighs]

387
00:16:31,157 --> 00:16:34,619
So, congratulations
are in order, but...

388
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:37,747
Well, the country's
still in a crisis.

389
00:16:37,788 --> 00:16:41,709
Just try not to get so caught up
in love and neglect training.

390
00:16:41,751 --> 00:16:44,212
If that was a concern
then why encourage me?

391
00:16:44,253 --> 00:16:45,129
[AUGUST chuckles]

392
00:16:45,171 --> 00:16:48,007
"I'll tell her how I feel
once the battle is over."

393
00:16:48,049 --> 00:16:49,300
I've read enough stories to know

394
00:16:49,342 --> 00:16:51,719
that the guy who says
that is gonna die.

395
00:16:51,761 --> 00:16:53,930
