a death flag?

396
00:16:58,559 --> 00:16:59,435
[SHIN]
'Kay!

397
00:16:59,477 --> 00:17:00,895
Listen up, everyone.

398
00:17:00,937 --> 00:17:03,856
We're gonna try out a brand new
form of magic training now.

399
00:17:03,898 --> 00:17:05,483
Wait, so we came
here to train?!

400
00:17:05,525 --> 00:17:07,944
Is it something we can
do in our swimsuits?

401
00:17:07,985 --> 00:17:08,778
Yeah.

402
00:17:08,819 --> 00:17:11,405
