this specially‐made ball.

403
00:17:12,490 --> 00:17:14,575
What do you suppose
they plan to do?

404
00:17:14,617 --> 00:17:16,410
I don't trust that boy.

405
00:17:16,452 --> 00:17:18,287
He's just having fun.

406
00:17:18,329 --> 00:17:21,207
So yeah, those are the rules.
Have questions?

407
00:17:21,249 --> 00:17:23,626
[LYN] We're free to use
our magic for this, right?

408
00:17:23,668 --> 00:17:26,420
Yeah, but you can only
have it target the ball.

409
00:17:26,462 --> 00:17:29,215
