I'll have to call it a foul.

410
00:17:31,676 --> 00:17:34,011
Don't do anything crazy
and get hurt!

411
00:17:34,053 --> 00:17:35,054
[ALICE]
Right!

412
00:17:35,096 --> 00:17:37,515
Okay! Here goes nothin'!

413
00:17:40,017 --> 00:17:40,851
Huh?!

414
00:17:40,893 --> 00:17:42,311
[ALICE grunts]

415
00:17:42,979 --> 00:17:44,105
[SHIN]
How did she...?

416
00:17:44,146 --> 00:17:47,024
Oh, right. Physical enhancement.

417
00:17:47,066 --> 00:17:50,736
[ALICE yells]

418
00:17:50,778 --> 00:17:52,780
[OLIVIA]
I've got it!

419
00:17:52,822 --> 00:17:55,157
That was really
well done, Olivia!

420
00:17:55,199 --> 00:17:58,369
Here we go!
Fury of the Tempest!

421
00:17:58,411 --> 00:17:59,829
Ha!

422
00:17:59,870 --> 00:18:00,913
[TONY]
How?!

423
00:18:00,955 --> 00:18:01,747
[MARIA]
Lyn!

424
00:18:01,789 --> 00:18:02,873
[LYN]
I'm there!

425
00:18:02,915 --> 00:18:06,168
Flame... Attack!

426
00:18:08,504 --> 00:18:11,215
[screams]

427
00:18:13,676 --> 00:18:15,636
Aw, dang it.
I dropped the ball.

428
00:18:15,678 --> 00:18:16,929
Not bad.

429
00:18:16,971 --> 00:18:18,097
[LYN sighs]

430
00:18:18,139 --> 00:18:19,348
