chew you up, and‐‐

441
00:18:40,661 --> 00:18:42,580
[ALICE]
Hey, look out!

442
00:18:43,289 --> 00:18:45,082
[BOTH scream]

443
00:18:45,124 --> 00:18:46,167
[MERLIN grunts]

444
00:18:48,502 --> 00:18:49,462
Thank you!

445
00:18:49,503 --> 00:18:51,255
Sorry about that. I slipped!

446
00:18:51,297 --> 00:18:53,758
I think that really
could've injured us.

447
00:18:55,176 --> 00:18:56,510
[MELIDA]
Shame on both of you!

448
00:18:56,552 --> 00:18:59,305
If you can't be careful, I will
ban you from this training!

449
00:18:59,347 --> 00:19:00,931
[LYN, ALICE]
We're very sorry.

450
00:19:00,973 --> 00:19:04,060
[MERLIN laughs]
It's fine. Everyone's safe.

451
00:19:04,101 --> 00:19:08,606
Besides, I think we just hit on
what this exercise is all about.

452
00:19:08,648 --> 00:19:10,608
You need to measure
your magic control

453
00:19:10,650 --> 00:19:14,195
